guy who lost his girl and who looked at the water and said it was
going to take a lot of river to get her out of his head,'' he said.
   ``I was always good in geography in school and I tossed in names
of three rivers that came to mind _ the Mississippi, the Ohio and
the Monongahela,'' said Kurhajetz, 46, an airlines agent from
