rising 3] to 56[ after a competing bid emerged to the
previously-disclosed $55 per share proposal from the Haft family.
   Schlumberger rose 1} to 34. The oil-service company announced
late Monday that would repurchase 30 million shares of common stock.
   Among the broader market indicators, the New York Stock Exchange
composite index of all listed issues rose 0.36 to 152.28. The
American Stock Exchange's market-value index rose 0.53 to 298.20.
